## ðŸ“„ Description
Dodge the Blocks is a simple browser-based arcade game where the player moves left and right to avoid falling blocks. The goal is to survive as long as possible and achieve a high score.

This game was developed as part of the **DC 101 â€“ Web Development** course to demonstrate skills in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

