## â–¶ Instructions to Run the Game
1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in any modern web browser.
3. Click **Start Game**.
4. Use the **Left Arrow** and **Right Arrow** keys to move.
5. Dodge the falling blocks to increase your score.